      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;backgrounds&#34;&gt;Backgrounds&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The docs module/layout was applied for the &lt;code&gt;docs&lt;/code&gt; section by default, it makes sense to separate the multiple digital gardens into different sections in most cases, such as docs for multiple projects, guides and notes.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-to-use-docs-layout-on-other-sections&#34;&gt;How to Use Docs Layout on other Sections?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To use the docs layout on sections other than &lt;code&gt;docs&lt;/code&gt;, what you need to do is to set the &lt;code&gt;type&lt;/code&gt; to &lt;code&gt;docs&lt;/code&gt; in front matter.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;config-toggle mb-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul class=&#34;nav nav-tabs mb-1&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item mb-0&#34; role=&#34;presentation&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;button&#xA;          class=&#34;nav-link active&#34;&#xA;          id=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-toml-tab&#34;&#xA;          data-bs-toggle=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;          data-bs-target=&#34;#code-toggle--147653298-toml&#34;&#xA;          type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;          role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;          aria-controls=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-toml&#34;&#xA;          aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;          TOML&#xA;        &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item mb-0&#34; role=&#34;presentation&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;button&#xA;          class=&#34;nav-link&#34;&#xA;          id=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-yaml-tab&#34;&#xA;          data-bs-toggle=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;          data-bs-target=&#34;#code-toggle--147653298-yaml&#34;&#xA;          type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;          role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;          aria-controls=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-yaml&#34;&#xA;          aria-selected=&#34;false&#34;&gt;&#xA;          YAML&#xA;        &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item mb-0&#34; role=&#34;presentation&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;button&#xA;          class=&#34;nav-link&#34;&#xA;          id=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-json-tab&#34;&#xA;          data-bs-toggle=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;          data-bs-target=&#34;#code-toggle--147653298-json&#34;&#xA;          type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;          role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;          aria-controls=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-json&#34;&#xA;          aria-selected=&#34;false&#34;&gt;&#xA;          JSON&#xA;        &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;tab-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div&#xA;        class=&#34;tab-pane fade show active&#34;&#xA;        id=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-toml&#34;&#xA;        role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&#xA;        aria-labelledby=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-toml-tab&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-toml&#34; data-lang=&#34;toml&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;docs&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div&#xA;        class=&#34;tab-pane fade&#34;&#xA;        id=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-yaml&#34;&#xA;        role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&#xA;        aria-labelledby=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-yaml-tab&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;l&#34;&gt;docs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div&#xA;        class=&#34;tab-pane fade&#34;&#xA;        id=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-json&#34;&#xA;        role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&#xA;        aria-labelledby=&#34;code-toggle--147653298-json-tab&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-json&#34; data-lang=&#34;json&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;   &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;type&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;docs&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
